|------|---------------|-------------|
| [promptService.js](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/services/promptService.js) | Lines 128, 129, 200, 260, 269, 270 | Every `.insert()`, `.select()`, `.ilike()` query uses `name` and `body` as raw strings |
| [AdminPromptForm.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/components/admin/AdminPromptForm.jsx) | Lines 11, 33-34 | Reads `editingPrompt.name`, sends `{ name, body }` to createPrompt |
| [AdminPromptRow.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/components/admin/AdminPromptRow.jsx) | Lines 52, 55 | Renders `prompt.name` and `prompt.body` |
| [PromptCard.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/components/PromptCard.jsx) | Lines 75, 117, 129, 139 | Copies `prompt.body`, displays `prompt.name` |
| [Landing.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/Landing.jsx) | Lines 56-57 | Search filter checks `p.name` and `p.body` |
| [Admin.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/Admin.jsx) | Lines 155-156 | Search filter checks `p.name` and `p.body` |
| [PublicVault.jsx](file:///d:/CODING/prompter/src/pages/PublicVault.jsx) | Lines 115-116 | Search filter checks `p.name` and `p.body` |
