### Difficulty to reach 10K readiness: 🔴 Significant rework required

It's not a matter of "add pagination and you're done." The missing piece is structural — **you have no backend layer at all**. Every feature that requires server-side processing (rate limiting, AI, webhooks, scheduled jobs, analytics aggregation, email notifications) is impossible to add without first building Supabase Edge Functions or a standalone API.

